summary: Use this api to get the selectable shipping_document_type and suggested shipping_document_type
description: Use this api to get the selectable shipping_document_type and suggested shipping_document_type.

query.name: booking_list
query.description: The list of bookings you want to get. limit [1,50]

query.name: booking_sn
query.description: Shopee's unique identifier for a booking.

query.name: tracking_number
query.description: The tracking number of booking. Required except for the channel allow print before arrange shipment.

query.name: shipping_document_type
query.description: The type of shipping document. Available values: NORMAL_AIR_WAYBILL,THERMAL_AIR_WAYBILL,NORMAL_JOB_AIR_WAYBILL,THERMAL_JOB_AIR_WAYBILL

request_examples.code:
<?php

$curl = curl_init();

curl_setopt_array($curl, array(
  CURLOPT_URL => 'https://open.admin.uat.shopee.io/api/v2/logistics/create_booking_shipping_document?access_token=access_token&partner_id=partner_id&shop_id=shop_id&sign=sign&timestamp=timestamp',
  CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER => true,
  CURLOPT_ENCODING => '',
  CURLOPT_MAXREDIRS => 10,
  CURLOPT_TIMEOUT => 0,
  CURLOPT_FOLLOWLOCATION => true,
  CURLOPT_HTTP_VERSION => CURL_HTTP_VERSION_1_1,
  CURLOPT_CUSTOMREQUEST => 'POST',
  CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS => '{
    "booking_list": [
        {
            "booking_sn": "201201E81SYYKE",
            "shipping_document_type": "NORMAL_AIR_WAYBILL",
            "tracking_number": "SPXID02742637123B"
        }
    ]
}',
  CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER => array(
    'Content-Type: application/json'
  ),
));

$response = curl_exec($curl);

curl_close($curl);
echo $response;
